Does a new supplement help people sleep better?

In a test, you would test both the real pill and a placebo and have testers take the pill/placebo each night for a week. Record how many hours they sleep each night.


Will new uniforms help a gym's business?

Do a survey where you measure the general excitement for the team. In one version, include all photos to old uniforms and in another, use photos and references for the new uniforms


Will a new homepage improve my online exotic pet rental business?

Push live the old homepage and the new homepage and randomly direct users to each. Track the amount of time spent on page and if they're likely to make a rental.


If I put 'please read' in the email subject will more people read my emails?

Put 'please read' on 5 emails then no 'please read' on 5 emails, track the open rate of the emails
